I wanted to stop grinding so bad... because I ain’t like how folks tried me and my manhood but I kept going 🙏🏾 Stayed focus & didn’t stop 🗣 I be looking at shit now like damn I did look like a lil bitch but hey mannnnn I was a child trying to provide. i wanted to feed my family I ain’t give a fuck about that other shit ‼️
